# Sales Prediction using Advertising Dataset

This project predicts product sales based on advertising expenditure on TV, Radio, and Newspaper using Machine Learning.

## Dataset
Features:
- TV
- Radio
- Newspaper

Target:
- Sales

## Model Used
- Linear Regression

## Evaluation Metrics
- MAE
- MSE
- R2 Score

## Conclusion
The Linear Regression model predicts sales accurately based on advertising data.
